Published Sunday, 2026-03-29, including PRs merged Friday, 2026-03-13 through Thursday, 2026-03-19.
—ЩRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2026-03-20-twin0343.mdЩ@67c9b0932050f327791731666b417fc8baaabe92a5aeda4b68b0fd02b4b7481bЩ"title: 'This week in Nushell #343'‘§NushellЪ№@smartcoder0777:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17837] fixed 
``group-by``
 behavior for lists/records (#17837)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17833] added --base support to 
``url parse``
 (#17833)
@fdncred:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17836] upgraded rmcp to version 1.2.0 (#17836)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17835] upgraded 
``glob``
 to use wax crate v0.7.0 (#17835)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17819] swapped order of user and default library directories, const $NU_LIB_DIRS (#17819)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17800] updated command docs to include command types (#17800)
@ysthakur:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17834] bumped reedline to latest main (#17834)
@musicinmybrain:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17832] updated lscolors from 0.20 to 0.21 (#17832)
@cptpiepmatz:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17825] fixed clippy issues (#17825)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17822] warned on 
``clippy::needless_raw_strings``
 (#17822)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17820] refactored more command integration tests (#17820)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17813] bumped 
``toml``
 crate to 1.0 (#17813)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17805] warned on 
``clippy::push_format_string``
 (#17805)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17804] gave 
``http get``
 tests with socks proxy more execution time (#17804)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17803] enabled 
``env_shlvl_in_repl``
 and 
``env_shlvl_in_exec_repl``
 tests (#17803)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17801] refactored 
``test_examples``
 usage with centralized testing (#17801)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17794] fixed 
``http``
 not respecting proxy vars like 
``ALL_PROXY``
 (#17794)
@hustcer:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17821] excluded nu-test-support for loongarch64 to fix release script (#17821)
@Rohan5commit:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17818] fixed devdocs wording (#17818)
@zhiburt:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17812] adjusted width estimation for header_on_border in nu-table (#17812)
@tauanbinato:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17811] fixed output type signatures for 
``hash md5``
 and 
``hash sha256``
 (#17811)
@Bahex:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17797] added 
``test_record!``
 convenience macro (#17797)
@ymcx:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17791] dropped mode preservation to fix copying read-only dirs (#17791)
@weirdan:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17788] added completions for 
``into binary --endian``
 (#17788)
@pickx:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17787] added 
``group-by``
 flag to delete column after grouping (#17787)
@blackhat-hemsworth:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17783] added duplicate histogram output column check (#17783)
@stuartcarnie:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17566] added configurable external hinter closure to repl (#17566)
@app/dependabot:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17831] bumped winreg from 0.55.0 to 0.56.0 (#17831)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17830] bumped scraper from 0.25.0 to 0.26.0 (#17830)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17774] bumped sqlparser from 0.60.0 to 0.61.0 (#17774)
